WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:06.000
Most small trades do not lose jobs because the quote was bad. They lose them because the follow-up gets buried.

00:06.000 --> 00:13.200
With Follow-Up Fix, you send three to five open quotes in rough notes.

00:13.200 --> 00:23.600
We turn them into one clean chase list: who is due today, who is overdue, and the exact message to copy.

00:23.600 --> 00:32.800
You send every message yourself from WhatsApp, text, or email. No CRM, no inbox access, and no card for the trial.

00:32.800 --> 00:36.940
Try it free for seven days. If it helps, keep it for nineteen pounds a month. If not, no payment needed.
